      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the high-revving 3.8L direct-fuel-injection (DFI) flat-six engine. This specimen is mechanically flawless, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle and the Sport Chrono Package Plus for optimized throttle mapping and dynamic engine mounts. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), ensuring precise damping and a 10mm lower ride height for superior lateral stability. The braking system, featuring four-piston aluminum monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors, remains in peak operational condition with no signs of thermal glazing. The exterior retains its factory-spec finish with zero paint correction required, while the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting a climate-controlled history. Comprehensive service logs confirm the integrity of the integrated dry-sump lubrication and cooling systems. A turn-key, concours-ready example for the discerning purist.",
